Package: webhose
Type: Package
Title: Tools to Work with the 'webhose.io' 'API'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Bob", "Rudis", email = "bob@rud.is", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Philipp", "Ottolinger", email = "philipp@ottolinger.de", role = "ctb"))
Maintainer: Bob Rudis <bob@rud.is>
Description: The 'webhose.io' <https::webhose.io/about> 'API' provides access to structured 
    web data feeds across vertical content domains. Their crawlers download the web, 
    structure the data and index save it into domain-specific repositories that can be
    accessed on demand. Methods are provided to query and retrieve content from this 'API'.
URL: https://github.com/hrbrmstr/webhose
BugReports: https://github.com/hrbrmstr/webhose/issues
License: AGPL
Suggests:
    testthat,
    covr
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    purrr, 
    tibble
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
